1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,300
We'll be taking all of our learnings throughout this course to build

2
00:00:03,300 --> 00:00:07,455
a full end-to-end project with datasets that have real-world importance.

3
00:00:07,455 --> 00:00:11,130
This project will test you on your data analysis process,

4
00:00:11,130 --> 00:00:12,840
how to post questions,

5
00:00:12,840 --> 00:00:16,395
investigate problems, and communicate results.

6
00:00:16,395 --> 00:00:18,915
To get started, you will be provided

7
00:00:18,915 --> 00:00:22,275
a workspace which will contain the dataset and then Jupiter notebook.

8
00:00:22,275 --> 00:00:25,725
You can conduct all of your project work in this workspace,

9
00:00:25,725 --> 00:00:28,755
which will make it easier for you to submit your work directly.

10
00:00:28,755 --> 00:00:31,275
If you prefer to do your project locally,

11
00:00:31,275 --> 00:00:34,710
you can download your project files and work on your local machine.

12
00:00:34,710 --> 00:00:38,050
Best of luck, on your project adventures.

